nhc_headline: ...OCTAVE MAINTAINS STRENGTH OVER THE OPEN TROPICAL EAST PACIFIC...
summary: ...OCTAVE MAINTAINS STRENGTH OVER THE OPEN TROPICAL EAST PACIFIC... As of 2:00 AM PDT Thu Oct 02 the center of Octave was located near 12.1, -117.9 with movement W at 8 mph. The minimum central pressure was 996 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 65 mph.
